name: Elite MTI Aleph 99
raw:
<font color=#009B00>

This Instruction Manual will teach you how to assemble a:
  'Elite MTI Aleph 99'
 The Construction kit. must be between Quality Level 200 and 200.
 All other pieces must be of AT LEAST that level range... 
 Add them using shift+right-click.
 Add the pieces in the following order:
 
  1. Submachinegun Weapons Construction kit.
 
  2. Ultra-Long Composite Barrel. . SkillTo Assemble: Weapon Smt: 850-850
 
  3. Notum Alloy Strengthened Ribs. . SkillTo Assemble: Mech. Engi: 500-500
 
  4. Lock and Stock. . SkillTo Assemble: Weapon Smt: 800-800
 
  5. Notum Enriched Nano Paste - 1x Layer. . SkillTo Assemble: Nano Progra: 300-300
 
  6. Nano Pylon. . SkillTo Assemble: Mech. Engi: 500-500
 
  7. Notum Enriched Nano Paste - 2x Layer. . SkillTo Assemble: Nano Progra: 400-400
 
  8. Stamina Cluster - Bright (Leg). . SkillTo Assemble: Nano Progra: 400-400
 
  9. Triple Pulse Enabler. . SkillTo Assemble: Weapon Smt: 850-850
 
  10. Explosion Propulsion Containment Chamber. . SkillTo Assemble: Mech. Engi: 700-700
 
  11. Nano Pylon. . SkillTo Assemble: Mech. Engi: 500-500
